search_results.title: Johanna Hill and Johanna Sturdy
search_results.snippet: Johanna Hill (d. 1441) and Johanna Sturdy (fl. 1459) were English bell-makers. They both ran the same bell-foundry in Aldgate, London in the fifteenth century.
